g.text: This workflow deploys a previously trained auto-regressive model for anomaly detection. The input data must include at least 2 months
of past values. This workflow calls a separate "Send_email_to _start_checkup" workflow in case of a 2nd level alarm.
Model deployment and calculating 1st level alarms
